Reporting / IP Check is a plugin that verifies
what internet knows about exposed public IP 
addresses - works with IPv4 and IPv6.
Includes widget. Only one API requires a (free)
API key.
***
It requires (at least) an access to ip4.seeip.org
in order to identify the public IP address of
OPNsense. Make sure that DNS resolver isn't blocking
seeip.org domain.
***